w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F17171339%2FScreen-Shot-2020-03-17-at-5.13.15-PM-1024x625.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-442023%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EShaheen%20Bagh%20on%20March%2010.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40UmarKhalidJNU%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDay%20in%20and%20day%20out%20bulldozers%20are%20on%20the%20streets%20to%20target%20the%20Muslim%20properties%2C%20on%20one%20or%20the%20other%20pretexts.%20In%20BJP%20ruled%20states%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20competition%20as%20to%20who%20can%20inflict%20more%20damage%20to%20Muslim%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20A.P.%20Shah%2C%20a%20retired%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%2C%20affirmed%20to%20the%20news%20portal%20%3Cem%3ECoda%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CMere%20alleged%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fcommentary%2Fbulldozer-justice-indian-state-lawlessness%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fcommentary%2Fbulldozer-justice-indian-state-lawlessness%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707906276176000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw03foE_iIGW3k1ya7pHryDZ%5C%22%3Einvolvement%20in%3C%2Fa%3E%20criminal%20activity%20cannot%20ever%20be%20grounds%20for%20demolition%20of%20property.%E2%80%9D%20While%20the%20cow%20politics%20has%20led%20to%20stray%20animals%20causing%20accidents%20on%20roads%20and%20in%20attacks%20on%20the%20standing%20crops%20on%20one%20hand%2C%20on%20the%20other%20it%20has%20led%20to%20initiation%20of%20a%20new%20phenomenon%20of%20lynching%20on%20Indian%20streets.%20Starting%20from%20Mohammad%20Akhlaq%20there%20are%20many%20cases%20where%20Muslims%20(and%20also%20Dalits)%20have%20been%20the%20target%20of%20the%20incited%20mobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20of%20Monu%20Manesar%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20crime%20of%20Nasir%20and%20Junaid%20is%20most%20frightening.%20Harsh%20Mander%20who%20visited%20victims%E2%80%99%20families%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20profoundly%20chilled%20as%20I%20scan%20social%20media%20pages%20of%20Monu%20Manesar.%20He%20and%20members%20of%20his%20gang%20live%20stream%20as%20they%20openly%20brandish%20sophisticated%20firearms%2C%20sound%20sirens%20mimicking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2Fmewat-killings-reveal-how-police-watch-armed-gangs-attack-muslims%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2Fmewat-killings-reveal-how-police-watch-armed-gangs-attack-muslims%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707906276177000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0uBCPM1rY1UBqN8vkCeiTI%5C%22%3Epolice%20jeeps%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20shoot%20at%20vehicles%2C%20and%20brutally%20thrash%20the%20men%20they%20catch.%E2%80%9D%20The%20proper%20data%20of%20bovine%20related%20violence%20is%20not%20available%20as%20the%20state%20wants%20to%20hide%20it%2C%20but%20it%20has%20created%20a%20fear%20among%20large%20sections%20of%20Muslims.%20In%20Mewat%20in%20particular%2C%20Muslims%20who%20deal%20with%20dairy%20business%20face%20a%20tough%20time.%20Just%20a%20couple%20of%20horrific%20incidents%20which%20give%20us%20chills%20in%20our%20spines%20are%20when%20Shambhulal%20Regar%20not%20only%20killed%20but%20videotaped%20the%20brutal%20killing%20of%20Afrazul%20in%20Rajasthan.%20We%20saw%20those%20accused%20of%20murdering%20Kalimuddin%20Ansari%20feted%20by%20Jayant%20Sinha%2C%20a%20Union%20minister%20at%20the%20time.%20Such%20incidents%20have%20now%20become%20the%20new%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20saw%20the%20scare%20created%20around%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20and%20then%20how%20types%20of%20jihad%20were%20tabulated%20%E2%80%93%20UPSC%20and%20land%20jihad%20among%20others.%20The%20amusing%20one%20was%20corona%20jihad%2C%20where%20the%20Tablighi%20Jamaat%20meeting%20was%20blamed%20for%20the%20spread%20of%20COVID-19%20and%20Muslims%20hawkers%20were%20denied%20entry%20into%20societies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIslamophobia%20is%20reaching%20new%20heights%20by%20the%20day.%20This%20intimidatory%20atmosphere%20is%20leading%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20process%20of%20ghettoisation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20cities.%20Muslims%20are%20being%20denied%20housing%20in%20the%20mixed%20localities%20in%20most%20places.%20This%20is%20accompanied%20by%20the%20decline%20in%20their%20educational%20and%20economic%20status.%20One%20example%20of%20this%20is%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Maulana%20Azad%20Fellowship%2C%20the%20major%20beneficiaries%20of%20which%20have%20been%20the%20Muslim%20students%20trying%20to%20pursue%20higher%20education.%20The%20economic%20climb-down%20of%20the%20community%20continues%20in%20recent%20years.%20Gallup%20data%20shows%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20both%20groups%2C%20(Hindus%20and%20Muslims)%20perceptions%20that%20standards%20of%20living%20were%20worsening%20shot%20up%20between%202018%20and%202019%2C%20as%20the%20Indian%20economy%20entered%20a%20deep%20slowdown.%20Among%20Muslim%20Indians%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Fpoll%2F396887%2Feconomic-pain-uneven-india-muslim-hindu-populations.aspx%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Fpoll%2F396887%2Feconomic-pain-uneven-india-muslim-hindu-populations.aspx%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1707906276177000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1NUzcQX_aaIMP_YSNOfnwn%5C%22%3Ethe%20percentage%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0jumped%20to%2045%25%20in%202019%2C%20up%20from%2025%25%20the%20previous%20year.%20And%20among%20Hindu%20Indians%2C%20the%20percentage%20saying%20the%20same%20hit%2037%25%20in%202019%2C%20an%20increase%20of%2019%20percentage%20points%20from%202018.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20threat%20of%20disenfranchising%20Muslims%20through%20the%20exercise%20of%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20and%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Acr%20is%20very%20much%20there.%20The%20Assam%20exercise%20showed%20that%20among%20the%2019%20lakh%20people%20who%20did%20not%20have%20proper%20papers%20the%20majority%20were%20Hindus.%20For%20Hindus%2C%20the%20safety%20clause%20of%20CAA%20is%20in%20place%20and%20for%20Muslims%2C%20detention%20centres%20are%20coming%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20show%20of%20sympathy%20for%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%20is%20mere%20eyewash.%20We%20understand%20the%20majority%20of%20victims%20of%20violence%20inspired%20by%20majoritarian%20politics%20are%20Pasmanda%20Muslims.%20The%20Muslim%20Ashrafs%20do%20need%20to%20ensure%20better%20treatment%20of%20the%20Pasmandas%2C%20but%20the%20bigger%20threat%20for%20the%20community%20as%20a%20whole%20is%20the%20insecurity%2C%20which%20affects%20them%20both%20and%20makes%20a%20fertile%20ground%20for%20orthodox%20elements%20to%20flourish.%20Reform%20amongst%20the%20Muslim%20community%20is%20a%20must.%20However%2C%20reforms%20remain%20in%20the%20backyard%20when%20the%20community%20feels%20a%20threat%20to%20its%20very%20existence%20and%20to%20the%20citizenship%20of%20its%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20government%20in%20different%20states%20is%20now%20planning%20things%20which%20are%20blatantly%20discriminatory%20against%20Muslims.%20With%20the%20Ram%20temple%20inaugurated%2C%20the%20RSS-BJP%E2%80%99s%20majoritarian%20politics%20may%20become%20more%20assertive.%20Already%2C%20Muslims%20have%20been%20losing%20representation%20in%20political%20institutions.%20We%20remember%20that%20in%20this%20Hindu%20nationalist%20party%20not%20a%20single%20MP%20is%20a%20Muslim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20earlier%20governments%20could%20not%20alleviate%20the%20suffering%20of%20this%20community.%20The%20major%20obstacle%20in%20this%20direction%20has%20been%20the%20opposition%20from%20RSS-BJP.%20The%20Sachar%20Committee%20has%20been%20an%20example%20of%20how%20any%20affirmative%20action%20for%20this%20deprived%20community%20is%20marred.%20In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20that%20report%2C%20the%20then%20Prime%20Mi