0on%20a%20training%20exercise%20with%20the%20Leibniz%20Institute%20for%20Baltic%20Sea%20Research%20Warnem%C3%BCnde%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20less%20than%20a%20meter%20high%20and%20consists%20of%20several%20large%20rocks%20linked%20together%20by%20more%20than%201%2C500%20smaller%20stones.%20The%20stones%20are%20aligned%20%26quot%3Bso%20regularly%20that%20a%20natural%20origin%20seems%20unlikely%2C%26quot%3B%20researchers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20used%20a%20multibeam%20sonar%20to%20map%20the%20seafloor%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Germany%20near%20to%20the%20town%20of%20Rerik.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfterwards%2C%20in%20the%20lab%2C%20we%20realized%20that%20there%20was%20this%20structure%20that%20looks%20not%20natural%2C%26quot%3B%20geophysicist%20Jacob%20Geersen%20at%20the%20Leibniz%20Institute%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newscientist.com%2Farticle%2F2416773-submerged-wall-could-be-the-largest-stone-age-megastructure-in-europe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20Scientist.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20only%20when%20we%20contacted%20the%20archaeologists%20that%20we%20understood%20it%20could%20be%20something%20significant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Blinkerwall%20was%20discovered%2021%20meters%20under%20the%20sea%2C%20which%20means%20it%20was%20likely%20to%20have%20been%20built%20before%20the%20last%20Ice%20Age%20ended%20around%208%2C500%20years%20ago%20as%20the%20sea%20level%20rose%20%26quot%3Bsignificantly%26quot%3B%20during%20this%20period%2C%20the%20article%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarlize%20Lombard%2C%20a%20professor%20and%20researcher%20of%20Stone%20Age%20Archaeology%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Johannesburg%2C%20told%20New%20Scientist%20that%20hunting%20walls%20were%20traditionally%20used%20to%20catch%20herds%20of%20animals%20such%20as%20antelope%2C%20who%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20run%20parallel%20to%20obstacles%20rather%20than%20jump%20over%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20believe%20this%20particular%20hunting%20wall%20was%20used%20to%20catch%20reindeer%2C%20which%20used%20the%20region%20as%20a%20habitat%2011%2C000%20years%20ago%2C%20according%20to%20the%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20is%20important%20because%20it%20could%20improve%20our%20knowledge%20of%20early%20hunter-gatherer%20communities%2C%20and%20how%20they%20survived.%20It%20could%20also%20allow%20scientists%20to%20find%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstoregga-tsunami-stone-age-population-decline-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStone%20Age%3C%2Fa%3E%20walls%20submerged%20by%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20were%20published%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1073%2Fpnas.2312008121%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProceedings%20of%20the%20National%20Academy%20of%20Sciences%3C%2Fa%3E%20journal%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstone-age-wall-humans-found-germany-baltic-sea-oldest-megastructure-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707827144000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cb55d194aa8ee8e84a84e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstone-age-wall-humans-found-germany-baltic-sea-oldest-megastructure-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20is%20thought%20to%20have%20been%20built%20in%20the%20Stone%20Age%20to%20channel%20reindeer%20into%20different%20areas%20by%20hunter-gatherers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfriel%40businessinsider.com%20(Mikhaila%20Friel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstone-age-wall-humans-found-germany-baltic-sea-oldest-megastructure-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%206-year-old%20United%20Airlines%20passenger%20was%20left%20scarre