2%3Eresulted%20in%20chaos%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20borders%20between%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Haryana%20and%20a%20traffic%20mess%20on%20the%20Delhi-UP%20border%20--%C2%A0%20from%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20governments%20of%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana.%20It%20has%20also%20made%20the%20Delhi%20government%20a%20party%20to%20the%20petitions%20and%20will%20hear%20its%20side%20during%20the%20next%20hearing%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Tuesday's%20hearing%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Acting%20Chief%20Justice%20GS%20Sandhawalia%20and%20Justice%20Lapita%20Banerji%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20has%20to%20be%20balance%20in%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20speech%20and%20expression%2C%20no%20right%20exists%20in%20isolation.%20The%20issue%20should%20be%20resolved%20amicably%20between%20all%20parties%20and%20areas%20should%20be%20identified%20by%20the%20states%20where%20the%20protest%20can%20be%20held...%20Use%20of%20force%20should%20be%20the%20last%20resort.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20observations%20came%20amid%20reports%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flive-updates-farmers-set-to-march-towards-delhi-borders-sealed-5047690%5C%22%3Edrones%20being%20used%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20drop%20tear%20gas%20on%20the%20farmers%20and%20the%20protestors%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftear-gas-fired-at-farmers-marching-towards-delhi-at-punjab-haryana-border-5048511%5C%22%3Ethrowing%20stones%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Right%20To%20Free%20Movement'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20PILs%20have%20been%20filed%20in%20the%20court%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20march.%20The%20first%20petition%20argued%20that%2C%20India%20being%20a%20democratic%20republic%2C%20preventing%20farmers%20from%20reaching%20Delhi%20and%20protesting%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20their%20right%20to%20free%20movement%2C%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20right%20to%20peaceful%20protest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20sought%20the%20lifting%20of%20internet%20suspension%20in%20seven%20districts%20of%20Haryana%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20prohibitory%20orders%20under%20Section%20144%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Procedure%20Code%20have%20been%20imposed%20in%2015%20districts%20of%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20reports%20of%20barbed%20wires%20being%20put%20up%20and%20nails%20being%20laid%20down%20on%20some%20roads%2C%20the%20petitioner%20said%20fundamental%20rights%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Constitution%20have%20been%20violated%20with%20the%20government%20stopping%20the%20farmers%20at%20various%20borders.%20The%20petition%20also%20highlighted%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20upheld%20the%20right%20to%20protest%20and%20assist%20in%20peaceful%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Cannot%20Cause%20Inconvenience'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20PIL%2C%20filed%20by%20a%20lawyer%2C%20Arvind%20Seth%2C%20argued%20that%20thousands%20of%20vehicles%20are%20moving%20towards%20Delhi%20and%20said%20that%20no%20one%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20block%20national%20highways.%20The%20petition%20claimed%20that%20people%20are%20facing%20inconvenience%20and%20even%20those%20going%20to%20hospitals%20are%20having%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(the%20farmers)%20can%20oppose%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20government%20but%20they%20cannot%20do%20so%20anywhere%20they%20choose%20and%20cause%20inconvenience%20to%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petition%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernments'%20Stand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20representing%20the%20Centre%20said%20the%20government%20is%20ready%20for%20negotiations%20with%20the%20farmers%2C%20including%20on%20their%20key%20issue%20of%20a%20law%20on%20minimum%20support%20price.%20The%20lawyer%20pointed%20out%20that%20a%20committee%20on%20MSP%20had%20been%20formed%20in%202022%20and%20the%20farmers%20had%20not%20sent%20their%20representatives.%20%26quot%3BMeetings%20can%20be%20held%20with%20the%20protesting%20farmers'%20representatives%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActing%20Chief%20Justice%20Sandhawalia%20then%20asked%20the%20Haryana%20government%20why%20it%20had%20blocked%20the%20borders%20when%20the%20farmers%20were%20passing%20through%20the%20state%2C%20and%20observed%20that%20they%20have%20the%20right%20to%20come%20and%20go.%20The%20state%20responded%20that%20it%20had%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%20since%20there%20was%20a%20call%20to%20gather%205%20km%20before%20the%20Delhi%20border%20and%20claimed%20that%20the%20farmers'%20tractors%20have%20been%20modified%20to%20include%20weaponry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20pointed%20out%20that%20Section%20144%20has%20been%20in%20force%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20since%20the%20last%20farmers'%20protest%2C%20where%20there%20had%20been%20some%20%26quot%3Bcriminal%20incidents%26quot%3B%20in%20Haryana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Punjab%20government%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20said%20there%20was%20merit%20in%20the%20farmers'%20demands%20and%20that%20it%20would%20allow%20peaceful%20protests.%20It%20said%20adequate%20arrangements%20have%20been%20made%20for%20crowd%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20all%20sides%2C%20the%20court%20said%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20have%20rights%20but%20the%20State%20also%20has%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20protect%20people%20on%20the%20roads%2C%20who%20have%20rights%20too.%20It%20said%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20should%20ensure%20that%20the%20protest%20is%20held%20only%20in%20designated%20places%20and%20urged%20all%20parties%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%20amicably%20before%20adjourning%20the%20matter%20till%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707826500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fgomrbat_punjab-farmers-delhi-protest_625x300_13_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news