Cspan%3EAppearing%20to%20underplay%20his%20exit%20from%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20a%20party%20which%20his%20family%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20for%20over%20five%20decades%20%E2%80%93%20Chavan%20said%20that%20he%20would%20not%20like%20to%20%E2%80%9Cget%20into%20a%20blame%20game%E2%80%9D%20and%20did%20not%20give%20a%20reason%20for%20his%20exit%2C%20instead%20saying%20he%20has%20now%20begun%20a%20new%20political%20journey%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChavan%20is%2065.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20him%2C%20another%20Congress%20leader%20%E2%80%93%20a%20former%20member%20of%20the%20legislative%20council%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Nanded%2C%20Amar%20Rajurkar%2C%20also%20joined%20BJP.%20Rajurkar%20was%20also%20present%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Mumbai%20which%20was%20jointly%20addressed%20by%20Chavan%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Devendra%20Fadnavis.%20Fadnavis%20announced%20that%20many%20other%20Congress%20leaders%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20dormant%20scam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChavan%2C%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Maharashtra%20for%20two%20short%20stints%20between%202008%20and%202010%2C%20had%20to%20abruptly%20step%20down%20following%20allegations%20of%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20Adarsh%20Co-operative%20Housing%20Society%20scam.%20The%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20investigating%20the%20case%2C%20had%20named%20him%20as%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20beneficiaries%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbombay-high-court-orders-demolition-of-adarsh-building-but-stays-order-for-three-months%5C%22%3Ea%2031-storey%20building%20which%20was%20originally%20built%20for%201999%20Kargil%20war%20heroes%20and%20fallen%20soldiers%E2%80%99%20war%20widows%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20central%20agency%20had%20claimed%20that%20a%20bunch%20of%20rules%20were%20violated%20in%20the%20process%20through%20which%20Chavan%E2%80%99s%20three%20relatives%20secured%20flats%20in%20this%20upmarket%20housing%20property%20in%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Cuffe%20Parade.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20been%20over%20a%20decade%20and%20a%20half%20since%20Chavan%20was%20named%20in%20the%20scam.%20The%20case%20has%20since%20remained%20dormant%2C%20with%20some%20of%20the%20primary%20accused%20of%20the%20case%20having%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FSpecials%2FlRcWV2Oa7UuS7JvuVe4ceK%2FAdarsh-scam-main-accused-Kanhaiyalal-Gidwani-64-dies.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edied%20in%20the%20meantime%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20has%20raked%20this%20issue%20up%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20In%202014%2C%20as%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%2C%20Adarsh%20grew%20into%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20poll%20planks%20for%20the%20party.%20And%20as%20recently%20as%20last%20week%2C%20when%20the%20Union%20finance%20ministry%20released%20its%20%E2%80%9Cwhite%20paper%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20Indian%20economy%2C%20the%20Adarsh%20scam%20once%20again%20found%20a%20mention%20under%20the%20section%20%E2%80%9Cpervasive%20corruption%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcentre-tables-white-paper-on-10-years-of-upa-hours-after-congresss-black-paper-on-modi-govts-failures%5C%22%3ECentre%20Tables%20White%20Paper%20on%2010%20Years%20of%20UPA%2C%20Hours%20After%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Black%20Paper%20on%20Modi%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20Failures%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20including%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20have%20attributed%20Chavan%E2%80%99s%20exit%20from%20the%20party%20to%20the%20pending%20trial%20in%20the%20case.%20Chavan%2C%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Mumbai%20soon%20after%20joining%20the%20BJP%2C%20called%20the%20Adarsh%20scam%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20accident%E2%80%9D.%20He%20denied%20any%20links%20between%20the%20scam%20and%20to%20his%20decision%20of%20quitting%20the%20Congress%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20series%20of%20exits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChavan%20is%20the%20third%20big%20name%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20after%20Milind%20Deora%20and%20Baba%20Siddique%2C%20to%20exit%20the%20party%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20While%20Deora%20went%20with%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Siddique%20hopped%20onto%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party.%20Reacting%20to%20Chavan%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20BJP%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fashok-chavan-called-me-baba-siddique-reveals-why-ex-cm-quit-congress-joined-bjp-101707818738288.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESiddique%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20this%20should%20come%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwake%20up%20call%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20senior%20Congress%20leader%2C%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%2C%20blamed%20the%20senior%20Congress%20leadership%20for%20Chavan%E2%80%99s%20exit.%20Chavan%E2%80%99s%20possible%20move%20to%20the%20BJP%20had%20been%20known%20for%20a%20while%20now.%20Nirupam%2C%20without%20mentioning%20any%20names%2C%20claimed%20that%20Chavan%20quit%20the%20party%20only%20because%20he%20was%20troubled%20by%20one%20particular%20party%20functionary.%20It%20is%20anybody%E2%80%99s%20guess%20that%20Nirupam%20was%20speaking%20about%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20chief%20Nana%20Patole.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20fact%2C%20all%20party%20leaders%20who%20spoke%20in%20favour%20of%20Chavan%20have%20blamed%20Patole%20for%20his%20style%20of%20running%20the%20party.%20Patole%2C%20who%20crossed%20over%20from%20the%20BJP%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20is%20known%20to%20have%20a%20strained%20relationship%20with%20most%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReacting%20to%20Chavan%E2%80%99s%20exit%2C%20Patole%20on%20Monday%2C%20February%2012%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20has%20given%20a%20lot%20to%20many%20leaders.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20today%2C%20when%20the%20party%20is%20fighting%20to%20save%20democracy%20and%20the%20Constitution%2C%20leaders%20who%20have%20got%20everything%20from%20it%20are%20quitting%20the%20party%20and%20its%20ideology.%20Who%20is%20going%20where%2C%20for%20what%3F%20The%20public%20is%20watching.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20To%20this%2C%20Chavan%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20it%20is%20true%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20given%20a%20lot%20to%20me%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20fact%20that%20I%20have%20given%20a%20lot%20to%20the%20Congress%20party.%20This%20truth%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20denied.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChavan%20is%20also%20the%20third%20prominent%20Maratha%20leader%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Before%20him%20Shinde%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20had%20both%20jumped%20boats.%20The%20BJP%20has%20tried%20hard%20to%20woo%20the%20Maratha%20community%20that%20is%20both%20numerically%20and%20politically%20dominant%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20has%20also%20meant%20alienation%20of%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20in%20the%20party.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20prominent%20leader%20from%20the%20OBC%20community%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal%2C%20who%20had%20left%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20to%20join%20Ajit%20Pawar%20is%20openly%20expressing%20his%20discontent%20with%20the%20BJP.%20He%20even%20rendered%20his%20resignation%20which%20the%20coalition%20government%20has%20not%20acted%20upon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707825546000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2