%3Cp%3EA%20man%20who%20flew%20from%20London%20to%20New%20York%20without%20any%20passport%20or%20boarding%20pass%20has%20been%20arrested%20after%20he%20failed%20to%20appear%20at%20a%20court%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-london-68275004%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Craig%20Sturt%20was%20arrested%20at%208%20am%20on%20Monday%20in%20Richmond%2C%20south-west%20London%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Metropolitan%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2046-year-old%20from%20Slough%2C%20Berkshire%2C%20is%20accused%20of%20passing%20through%20Heathrow%20Airport's%20security%20checks%20without%20showing%20credentials%20before%20boarding%20a%20British%20Airways%20flight%20to%20John%20F%20Kennedy%20Airport%20on%20December%2023%20last%20year%20without%20a%20passport%20or%20boarding%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20stopped%20on%20arrival%20at%20the%20John%20F%20Kennedy%20Airport%20and%20sent%20back%20to%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20where%20he%20was%20charged%20with%20fraud%20and%20offences%20under%20the%20Aviation%20Security%20Act.%20He%20was%20originally%20taken%20into%20custody%20on%20Christmas%20Day%20at%20approximately%208%3A00%20pm.%20following%20his%20return%20flight%20to%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritish%20Airways%20stated%20that%20he%20was%20aiding%20the%20authorities%20with%20their%20inquiry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Heathrow%20Airport%20spokesman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20people%20who%20go%20airside%20are%20subject%20to%20security%20screening%2C%20including%20the%20individual%20involved%20in%20this%20case.%20We%20are%20supporting%20the%20authorities%20with%20their%20ongoing%20investigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20British%20Airways%20flight%20from%20London%20to%20Prague%20was%20forced%20to%20turn%20around%20and%20make%20an%20emergency%20landing%20after%20fumes%20were%20observed%20in%20the%20cockpit%20on%20January%2022.%20According%20to%20Metro%2C%20the%20plane%20took%20off%20from%20Heathrow%20Airport%20at%207.25%20am%20on%20Sunday%20and%20was%20expected%20to%20land%20in%20Prague%20just%20after%2010%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20half%20an%20hour%20into%20the%20flight%2C%20it%20turned%20around%20over%20the%20Strait%20of%20Dover%20and%20came%20back%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20according%20to%20flight%20path%20data%20from%20FlightRadar24.%20The%20plane%20flew%20back%20to%20Heathrow%20and%20touched%20down%20at%208.41%20am.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20the%20plane%20landed%2C%20several%20fire%20engines%20rushed%20towards%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20British%20Airways%20spokesperson%20blamed%20a%20'technical%20issue'%20for%20the%20quick%20about-turn%2C%20though%20they%20did%20not%20specify%20what%20had%20caused%20the%20pilots%20to%20choose%20to%20return%20to%20Heathrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritish%20Airways%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20''We're%20sorry%20for%20the%20delay%20in%20our%20customers'%20journey%20after%20the%20aircraft%20returned%20to%20Heathrow%20as%20a%20precaution.%20Our%20teams%20looked%20after%20them%20whilst%20they%20waited%20to%20board%20a%20replacement%20aircraft%20to%20continue%20their%20journey.''%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707820800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fg2ms7k1o_british-airways_625x300_08_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-who-flew-from-london-to-new-york-without-a-passport-arrested-by-cops-5049824%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22British%20Airways%20stated%20that%20he%20was%20aiding%20the%20authorities%20with%20their%20inquiry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-who-flew-from-london-to-new-york-without-a-passport-arrested-by-cops-5049824%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-who-flew-from-london-to-new-york-without-a-pa