2%80%99%20in%20the%20operational%20capabilities%20of%20the%20Indo-Tibetan%20Border%20Police%20(ITBP)%2C%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20and%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2024%2FFeb%2F13%2Fconsultant-for-building-competencies-for-itbp-bsf-assam-rifles-likely-soon%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20reported%20that%20the%20aim%20of%20this%20move%20is%20to%20strengthen%20the%20border%20management%20system%20in%20the%20northern%20and%20eastern%20frontiers%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20consultant%2C%20officials%20told%20the%20daily%20that%20the%20government%20is%20looking%20for%20a%20retired%20defence%20officer%20to%20be%20inducted%20on%20contractual%20basis%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9CLevel%2014%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20candidate%20should%20have%20adequate%20experience%20in%20handling%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20border%20areas%2C%20besides%20handling%20security%20related%20matters%20and%20implementation%20of%20the%20policies%20envisaged%20for%20adequate%20development%20of%20the%20border%20areas%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20Kashmir%2C%20Sikkim%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20would%20also%20coordinate%20with%20agencies%20for%20implementing%20development%20works%20in%20border%20areas%2C%20including%20the%20centrally%20sponsored%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1985867%5C%22%3EVibrant%20Village%20Programme.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20the%20consultant%20would%20be%20required%20to%20carry%20out%20capacity%20needs%20analysis%20and%20mapping%20of%20the%20capacity%20building%20interventions%2C%20which%20are%20specific%20to%20the%20threat%20perception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consultant%20would%20also%20be%20mandated%20to%20conduct%20a%20comprehensive%20need%20assessment%20to%20understand%20the%20current%20and%20future%20challenges%20faced%20by%20border%20guarding%20forces%20and%20to%20identify%20stakeholder%20requirements%20and%20expectations%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20or%20she%20would%20also%20examine%20the%20%E2%80%98gap%20analysis%E2%80%99%20to%20identify%20areas%20where%20existing%20competencies%20fall%20short%20of%20requirements%20and%20recommend%20strategies%20to%20plug%20in%20this%20in%20the%20border%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20PIB%2C%20the%20government%20launched%20the%20Vibrant%20Village%20Programme%20on%20February%2015%2C%202023%2C%20with%20a%20financial%20outlay%20of%20Rs%204%2C800%20crore%20for%20the%20financial%20years%202022-23%20to%202025-26.%20The%20programme%20aims%20to%20comprehensively%20develop%20select%20villages%20in%2046%20blocks%20across%2019%20districts%20adjacent%20to%20the%20northern%20border%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20and%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707816619000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2Fbattalion.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovt-to-appoint-consultant-for-enhancing-operational-capabilities-of-itbp-bsf-and-assam-rifles%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Officials%20told%20the%20'New%20Indian%20Express'%20that%20the%20government%20is%20looking%20for%20a%20retired%20defence%20officer%20to%20be%20inducted%20on%20contractual%20basis%20at%20the%20'Level%2014'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovt-to-appoint-consultant-for-enhancing-operational-capabilities-of-itbp-bsf-and-assam-rifles%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BCCI%20Issues%20Strict%20Ranji%20Trophy%20Mandate%20Amid%20Ishan%20Kishan%20Row%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20has%20reportedly%20issued%20a%20strong%20mandate%20to%20its%20players%20who%20are%20not%20part%20of%20international%20assignments%20or%20undergoing%20rehab%20at%20the%20National%20Cricket%20Academy.%20The%20board%20wants%20all%20the%20fit%20players%2C%20not%20playing%20for%20the%20senior%20national%20team%2C%20to%20feature%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20for%20their%20teams.%20The%20verdict%20comes%20from%20the%20Indian%20board%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20debate%20around%20the%20situation%20of%20wicket-keeper%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20remains%20reluctant%20to%20play%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20despite%20being%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20leaving%20the%20South%20Africa%20tour%20midway%2C%20owing%20to%20mental%20fatigue%2C%20Ishan%20hasn't%20featured%20in%20any%20competitive%20cricket%20match.%20He%20was%20last%20seen%20practicing%20with%20his%20Mumbai%20Indians%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20Reliance%20Stadium.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20there%20being%20a%20clear%20directive%20from%20Team%20India%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20play%20'some%20sort%20of%20cricket'%2C%20Ishan%20continues%20to%20play%20by%20his%20own%20rules.%C2%A0The%20player%20reportedly%20decided%20to%20train%20in%20Baroda%20instead%20of%20playing%20for%20his%20state%20team%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy.%20The%20decision%20is%20said%20to%20have%20left%20many%20in%20the%20BCCI%20upset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA