0of%20the%20COP28%20summit%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EG-20%20New%20Delhi%20Leaders'%20Declaration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20G20%20summit%20held%20under%20India's%20presidency%20in%20September%20last%20year%20adopted%20a%20consensus%20declaration%20overcoming%20major%20differences%20on%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20called%20for%20ending%20the%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20trust%20deficit%26quot%3B.%20The%20big%20development%20was%20welcomed%20by%20several%20leaders%20and%20officials%2C%20who%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%26quot%3B%20document%20recognises%20PM%20Modi's%20emphasis%20on%20human-centric%20globalisation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuying%20Oil%20From%20Russia%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20the%20West%20had%20slapped%20stringent%20financial%20sanctions%20on%20Russia%20for%20its%202022%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20India%20increased%20the%20purchase%20of%20discounted%20crude%20oil%20from%20Moscow.%20India%20has%20maintained%20that%20as%20one%20of%20the%20top%20importers%20of%20crude%2C%20it%20will%20buy%20oil%20from%20anywhere%20it%20can%20strike%20a%20good%20bargain.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOperation%20Ganga%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20government%20undertook%20what%20looked%20like%20a%20massive%20challenge%20to%20rescue%20Indian%20students%20from%20Ukraine%20which%20was%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20war%20with%20Russia%20in%20February%20last%20year.%20The%20operation%20was%20called%20'Operation%20Ganga'.%20%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20behind%20the%20naming%20was%20that%20just%20the%20way%20Ganga%20is%20called%20Ma%20Ganga%2C%20it%20protects%20us%2C%20similarly%20this%20rescue%20operation%20was%20to%20protect%20and%20bring%20back%20its%20children%20to%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20had%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOperation%20Vande%20Bharat%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%20operated%20several%20flights%20under%20'Vande%20Bharat%20Mission'%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20Indians%20stranded%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20world%20due%20to%20coronavirus%20pandemic.%20The%20operation%20was%20launched%20in%20May%202020%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20Indians%20in%20a%20phased%20manner.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOperation%20'Samudra%20Setu'%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Indian%20Navy%20had%20also%20launched%20Operation%20'Samudra%20Setu'%20(sea%20bridge)%20to%20rescue%20Indian%20citizens%20from%20overseas%20amid%20cotronavirus-induced%20travel%20restrictions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOperation%20Sanjeevani%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20international%20borders%20were%20closed%20due%20to%20the%20coronavirus%20pandemic%20in%20April%202020%2C%20Operation%20Sanjeevani%20was%20launched%20to%20meet%20the%20medical%20requirements%20of%20Maldives.%20Under%20this%20operation%2C%20a%20special%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20plane%20airlifted%206.2%20tonnes%20of%20essential%20medical%20supplies%20from%20India%20to%20the%20Maldives.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EVaccine%20Diplomacy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndia%20shipped%20free%20COVID-19%20vaccine%20to%20several%20countries%20when%20the%20world%20was%20battling%20the%20pandemic.%20The%20move%C2%A0helped%20India%20gain%20political%20influence%20across%20the%20developing%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOperation%20Ajay%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20India%20launched%20Operation%20Ajay%20to%20facilitate%20the%20return%20of%20citizens%20from%20Israel%20amid%20a%20full-blown%20war%20with%20the%20Hamas%20group%20in%20Gaza%20last%20year.%20Special%20charter%20flights%20and%20other%20arrangements%20were%20put%20in%20place%20to%20evacuate%20the%20Indian%20nationals.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWing%20Commander%20Abinandan%20Varthaman's%20Return%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%20in%202019%20successfully%20secured%20the%20release%20of%20Air%20Force%20pilot%20Abhinandan%20Varthaman%20who%20was%20captured%20by%20Pakistani%20authorities%20after%20his%20MiG%2021%20was%20shot%20during%20an%20aeri