0has%20also%20deployed%20drones%20to%20keep%20a%20watch%20and%20record%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20could%20be%20seen%20covering%20their%20faces%20with%20clothes%20and%20masks%20to%20save%20themselves%20from%20the%20tear%20gas.%20The%20farmers%20a%20waiting%20for%20union%20leaders%20to%20reach%20the%20Shambu%20border%2C%20after%20which%20they%20will%20cross%20over%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20shared%20by%20farmers%2C%20many%20could%20be%20seen%20finding%20it%20hard%20to%20breathe.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20finding%20it%20hard%20to%20breathe%20and%20have%20stopped%20for%20a%20while.%20For%20the%20time%20being%2C%20we%20have%20been%20asked%20by%20the%20farmer%20union%20leaders%20to%20stop%20till%20they%20give%20us%20the%20green%20signal%20to%20move%20ahead%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20group%20of%20farmers%20in%20a%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20young%20farmer%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20front%20near%20the%20Shambu%20border%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20the%20China%20or%20Pakistan%20border%20but%20look%20how%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20barricaded%20the%20entire%20border.%20We%20are%20not%20asking%20for%20anything%20unjust.%20It%20is%20our%20legitimate%20right.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20call%20for%20Delhi%20Chalo%20was%20given%20by%20the%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%20and%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(non-political)%20led%20by%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20and%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%2C%20respectively%2C%20and%20other%20unions.%20Before%20leaving%20for%20Delhi%2C%20the%20farmers%20also%20held%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20BBC%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20laid%20multi-layered%20blocks%20at%20Singhu%2C%20Tikri%20and%20Ghazipur%20borders%2C%20which%20are%20the%20key%20intersections%20to%20reach%20Delhi%20on%20the%20road%20from%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana.%20The%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20also%20installed%20CCTV%20cameras%20at%20multiple%20locations%20at%20these%20three%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%202020%2C%20farmers%20had%20set%20up%20tents%20and%20parked%20their%20tractor-trailers%20at%20these%20borders%20for%20over%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20the%20Haryana%20police%E2%80%99s%20action%2C%20the%20Punjab%20Police%20was%20seen%20facilitating%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20march%20at%20various%20locations%20and%20ensured%20that%20both%20the%20farmers%20and%20other%20commuters%20did%20not%20face%20any%20difficulty.%20KMM%20coordinator%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20also%20managed%20the%20traffic.%20Standing%20on%20top%20of%20a%20moving%20vehicle%2C%20Pandher%20was%20seen%20addressing%20the%20farmers%20cavalcade.%20%E2%80%9CPlease%20maintain%20discipline%20and%20move%20in%20a%20line%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20kept%20repeating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20led%20by%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20Modi%20government%20for%20laying%20concertina%20wires%20and%20arranging%20drones%2C%20tear%20gas%2C%20nails%20and%20guns%20to%20counter%20the%20farmers.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20broken%20three%20promises%20which%20it%20had%20made%20to%20the%20farmers%3A%20doubling%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20by%202022%2C%20implementing%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20report%20and%20an%20MSP%20law.%20%E2%80%9CTime%20has%20come%20to%20raise%20voice%20for%2062%20crore%20farmers%20of%20the%20country.%20Congress%20will%20raise%20%E2%80%98Kisan%20Nyay%E2%80%99%20at%20Chattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Ambikapur%20today.%20We%20support%20farmers%20protest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20from%20the%20Punjab%20Congress%2C%20MLA%20Sukhpal%20Singh%20Khaira%20also%20went%20live%20on%20Facebook%20and%20announced%20that%20he%20will%20be%20proceeding%20towards%20the%20Shambu%20border%20to%20support%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20agitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20pictures%20of%20sealed%20borders%2C%20Khaira%20questioned%20whether%20this%20is%20how%20the%20government%20should%20treat%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20extreme%20cruelty%20with%20farmers%20who%20not%20only%20made%20India%20food%20sufficient%2C%20but%20remember%20its%20their%20sons%20who%20protect%20the%20borders%20in%20defence%20forces.%20Yet%20such%20barbarism%20against%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20too%20rejected%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20to%20convert%20Bawana%20Stadium%20into%20a%20temporary%20jail%20in%20view%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20Delhi%20Chalo%20march.%20Delhi%20government%20home%20minister%20Kailash%20Gahlot%20came%20out%20in%20support%20of%20the%20farmers%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20demands%20of%20the%20farmers%20are%20genuine.%20Secondly%2C%20it%20is%20the%20constitutional%20right%20of%20every%20citizen%20to%20peacefully%20protest.%20It%20is%20therefore%20incorrect%20to%20arrest%20the%20farmers.%20The%20Central%20government%20in%20fact%20should%20invite%20them%20over%20for%20talks%20and%20try%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20their%20genuine%20demands.%20Farmers%20of%20the%20country%20are%20our%20%3Cem%3Eannadata%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20treating%20them%20in%20this%20way%20by%20arresting%20them%20would%20be%20like%20rubbing%20salt%20into%20their%20wounds.%20We%20cannot%20be%20party%20to%20this%20decision.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20before%20beginning%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20march%2C%20KMM%20coordinator%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20and%20Bharti%20Kisan%20Union%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%20spokesperson%20Tejveer%20Singh%20Ambala%20held%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%2C%20Pandher%20said%20that%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20was%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20are%20acting%20as%20opposition%20in%20the%20country.%20Anybody%20including%20the%20senior%20farmer%20union%20leaders%20of%20SKM%2C%20who%20led%20the%20previous%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%2C%20are%20free%20to%20join%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejveer%20Ambala%20said%20that%20within%20one%20hour%20of%20the%20late-night%20meeting%2C%20they%20had%20realised%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20fulfilling%20their%20demands.%20%E2%80%9COur%20demand%20is%20an%20MSP%20guarantee%20law%2C%20justice%20for%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20victims%2C%20waiving%20off%20loans%20of%20the%20farmers%20and%20compensation%20to%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%20We%20will%20not%20return%20home%20without%20getting%20these%20demands%20fulfilled%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707814575000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13142417%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-2.14.07-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fpolice-use-tear-gas-on-protesting-farmers-at-punjab-haryana-border%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Farmers%20were%20breaking%20and%20removing%20barricades%20at%20the%20border%20when%20the%20police%20fired%20tear%20gas%20at%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fpolice-use-tear-gas-on-protesting-farmers-at-punjab-haryana-border%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmers%20Protest%3A%20Multiple%20Gates%20At%209%20Stations%20Of%20Delhi%20Metro%20Shut%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20view%20of%20the%20farmers'%20march%20to%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20one%20or%20more%20gates%20at%20eight%20stations%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Metro%20were%20shut%20on%20Tuesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20these%20stations%20are%20not%20closed%20and%20entry%20and%20exit%20of%20passengers%20is%20permitted%20through%20other%20gates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficial%20sources%20said%20the%20gates%20have%20been%20shut%20for%20security%20arrangements%20on