gland%20%26amp%3B%20Wales%20Cricket%20Board%20issued%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20advised%2C%20on%20returning%20to%20India%2C%20that%20there%20was%20paperwork%20discrepancy%20with%20Rehan%20Ahmed's%20visa.%20The%20local%20authorities%20at%20Rajkot%20Airport%20were%20supportive%2C%20enabling%20Rehan%20entry%20on%20a%20temporary%20visa.%20The%20correct%20visa%20should%20be%20processed%20and%20issued%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20He%20will%20continue%20to%20prepare%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20squad%20ahead%20of%20the%20third%20Test%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ECB%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20five-match%20Test%20series%20is%20poised%20at%201-1%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20first%20two%20Tests.%20The%20third%20match%20of%20the%20series%20will%20be%20played%20at%20Saurashtra%20Cricket%20Association%20Stadium%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20media%20reports%2C%20England%20travelled%20to%20Abu%20Dhabi%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20second%20Test%20at%20Visakhapatnam%20as%20there%20was%20a%2010-day%20gap%20between%20the%20second%20and%20third%20match%20of%20the%20series.%20While%20returning%2C%20Rehan%20was%20stopped%20at%20the%20Airport%20as%20he%20only%20held%20a%20single-entry%20visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20BCCI%20official%20has%20asserted%20that%20the%20visitors%20have%20been%20advised%20to%20process%20the%20player's%20visa%20again%20in%20the%20next%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20England%20team%20has%20been%20advised%20to%20process%20the%20visa%20again%20which%20will%20be%20happening%20in%20the%20next%20two%20days.%20The%20player%20was%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20country%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20team%20and%20he%20will%20be%20appearing%20in%20practice%20on%20Tuesday%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BCCI%20official%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20ESPNcricinfo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERehan%20has%20played%20both%20matches%20of%20the%20ongoing%20se