ntial%20of%20impacting%20the%20core%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20(core%20inflation)%20is%20a%2050-month%20low%20and%20suggests%20that%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20monetary%20policy%20perhaps%20is%20working%20by%20compressing%20the%20demand.%20But%20the%20headline%20is%20still%20higher%20than%20the%20targeted%204%25%20due%20to%20higher%20food%20inflation%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20worry%20area%20for%20RBI%20because%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20of%20impacting%20the%20core%20inflation%20via%20wage-price%20spiral%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20note%20by%20India%20Ratings%E2%80%99%20principal%20economist%20Sunil%20Kumar%20Sinha%20and%20senior%20analyst%20Paras%20Jasrai%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrban%20food%20inflation%20moderated%20to%209.02%25%20in%20January%20from%2010.42%25%20in%20December.%20Rural%20areas%20registered%207.91%25%20food%20inflation%20in%20January%20as%20against%208.49%25%20in%20the%20previous%20month%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707807648000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13122407%2Fimage-1826.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fjanuary-retail-inflation-hits-three-month-low-at-5-1-as-food-prices-rise-slowly-govt-data%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22However%2C%20this%20time%20as%20well%20rural%20inflation%20remained%20higher%20than%20urban%20areas.%20In%202022-23%2C%20rural%20inflation%20was%20higher%20than%20urban%20inflation%20for%20the%20entire%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fjanuary-retail-inflation-hits-three-month-low-at-5-1-as-food-prices-rise-slowly-govt-data%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Katy%20Perry%20Set%20to%20Exit%20%E2%80%98American%20Idol%E2%80%99%20After%20This%20Season%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1