gagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsweden-man-missing-and-twelve-people-injured-as-huge-fire-breaks-out-at-lisebergs-oceana-water-park-in-gothenburg-13070471%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsweden-man-missing-and-twelve-people-injured-as-huge-fire-breaks-out-at-lisebergs-oceana-water-park-in-gothenburg-13070471%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsweden-man-missing-and-twelve-people-injured-as-huge-fire-breaks-out-at-lisebergs-oceana-water-park-in-gothenburg-13070471%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indonesia%20Elections%3A%20What%20You%20Need%20To%20Know%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112512%2Fimage-1825.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIndonesia%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20Muslim-majority%20nation%2C%20is%20holding%20elections%20on%20February%2014%2C%20in%20which%20people%20will%20cast%20their%20ballots%20to%20elect%20not%20only%20a%20new%20president%20and%20vice%20president%20but%20also%20members%20of%20parliament%20and%20local%20legislative%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20is%20a%20massive%20undertaking%2C%20with%20over%20204%20million%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20270%20million%20people%20registering%20to%20vote%20across%20an%20archipelago%20made%20up%20of%20some%2017%2C000%20islands.%20The%20voters%20are%20spread%20across%20three%20time%20zones%2C%20from%20Papua%20in%20the%20east%20to%20the%20tip%20of%20Sumatra%20over%205%2C000%20kilometers%20(3%2C000%20miles)%20away%20in%20the%20west.%20Young%20people%20make%20up%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20registered%20voters%2C%20with%20some%2055%25%20of%20them%20aged%20between%2017%20and%2040%2C%20according%20to%20the%20General%20Elections%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncumbent%20President%20Joko%20Widodo%2C%20better%20known%20as%20Jokowi%2C%20is%20finishing%20his%20second%20term%20in%20office%20and%20cannot%20run%20again%20because%20of%20term%20limits.%20This%20year%E2%80%99s%20vote%20will%20thus%20lead%20to%C2%A0the%20first%20change%20in%20leadership%20in%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20are%20the%20presidential%20candidates%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20candidates%20are%20going%20to%20succeed%20Jokowi%20as%20president%3A%20Ganjar%20Pranowo%20and%20Anies%20Baswedan%2C%20both%20former%20governors%20in%20their%2050s%2C%20and%20Prabowo%20Subianto%2C%20the%20current%20defense%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubianto%20is%20a%2072-year-old%20former%20army%20special%20forces%20commander%20who%20is%20running%20for%20the%20top%20job%20for%20a%20third%20time.%20He%20lost%20to%20Jokowi%20in%202014%20and%202019.%20To%20cement%20his%20chances%20this%20time%20round%2C%20Subianto%20has%20roped%20in%20the%20hugely%20popular%20president%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Gibran%20Rakabuming%20Raka%2C%20as%20his%20running%20mate%20for%20vice%20president.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0The%20candidacy%20of%C2%A036-year-old%20Raka%2C%20who%20is%20half%20Subianto%E2%80%99s%20age%20and%20currently%20serving%20as%20mayor%20in%20Surakarta%20city%2C%20is%20seen%20by%20many%20analysts%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%C2%A0secure%20more%20votes%20from%20the%20younger%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubianto%20also%20hails%20from%20an%20elite%20political%20family.%20He%20was%20once%20the%20son-in-law%20of%20Suharto%2C%20a%20military%20dictator%20who%20was%20ousted%20from%20power%20in%201998%20after%20over%20three%20decades%20of%20rule.%C2%A0%20Subianto%20is%20accused%20of%20rights%20abuses%20while%20serving%20as%20a%20military%20chief%20during%20the%20dying%20days%20of%20the%20Suharto%20dictatorship.%20The%20allegations%20are%20unproven%2C%20and%20Prabowo%20has%20always%20denied%20any%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanjar%20Pranowo%2C%20another%20candidate%2C%20is%20a%20former%20governor%20of%20Central%20Java%20Province.%C2%A0%20His%20presidential%20bid%20is%20backed%20by%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20Indonesian%20Democratic%20Party%20of%20Struggle%20(PDI-P).%20Pranowo%20has%20announced%20incumbent%20Cabinet%20minister%20Mahfud%20Md%20as%20his%20running%20mate.%20Pranowo%20adopted%20the%20political%20style%20of%20President%20Widodo%20by%20trying%20to%20gain%20sympathy%20from%20grassroots%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20presidential%20hopeful%20is%20Anies%20Baswedan%2C%20former%20governor%20of%20the%20Indonesian%20capital%2C%20Jakarta.%20His%20running%20mate%20is%20Muhaimin%20Iskandar%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20Islamic%20National%20Awakening%20Party%20(PKB)%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20Islamic%20parties%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%20In%202017%2C%20Baswedan%20ran%20for%20governor%20of%20Jakarta%20against%20Basuki%20Tjahaja%20Purnama%2C%20who%20is%20of%20Chinese%20heritage.%20Baswedan%20won%20the%20election%20%E2%80%94%20while%20his%20competitor%20was%20sentenced%20two%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20blaspheming%20the%20Quran%20during%20one%20of%20his%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20latest%20surveys%20by%20Litbang%20Kompas%2C%20an%20independent%20research%20organization%2C%20Subianto%20is%20enjoying%20a%20considerable%20lead%20over%20the%20other%20two%20candidates%2C%20with%20about%2039%25%20of%20voters%20polled%20backing%20him%20compared%20to%2018%25%20for%20Pranowo%20and%20around%2016%25%20for%20Baswedan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20key%20issues%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20presidential%20hopefuls%20have%20made%20similar%20pledges%20on%20inclusive%20growth%20and%20welfare.%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20decade%20in%20office%20is%20generally%20seen%20as%20one%20of%20stability%20and%20growth%20for%C2%A0Southeast%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20economy.%20And%20the%20three%20contenders%20have%20pledged%20to%20continue%20most%20of%20his%20initiatives%2C%20including%20boosting%20mining%2C%20expanding%20social%20welfare%20and%20continuing%20work%20on%20building%20a%20%2432%20billion%20(%E2%82%AC29.7%20billion)%20new%20capital%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20candidates%20have%20set%20ambitious%20economic%20expansion%20targets%20and%20pledged%20to%20create%20millions%20of%20jobs%2C%20without%20giving%20out%20specific%20details%20as%20to%20how%20they%20will%20reach%20these%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20can%20vote%20and%20when%20can%20we%20expect%20the%20results%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20Indonesian%20citizens%20who%20are%2017%20or%20older%20can%20vote.%C2%A0%20Following%20decades%20of%20authoritarian%20rule%2C%20Indonesia%20embraced%20democracy%20in%201998%20and%20adopted%20a%20national%20philosophy%20of%20equality%20and%20national%20unity%20called%20Pancasila%2C%20which%20is%20enshrined%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20Muslim-majority%20country%2C%20it%20is%20constitutionally%20a%20secular%20state%20with%20a%20separation%20of%20religion%20and%20state.%20Nevertheless%2C%20political%20parties%20often%20employ%20religion%20in%20their%20campaign%20tactics.%C2%A0%20The%20nation%E2%80%99s%20parliament%20plays%20a%20relatively%20subordinate%20role%20in%20decision-making%2C%20with%20policy-making%20power%20resting%20with%20the%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20election%20rules%2C%20presidential%20candidates%20need%2050%25%20of%20the%20overall%20vote%20and%20at%20least%2020%25%20of%20votes%20in%20each%20province%20to%20win%20the%20vote.%C2%A0%20To%20enter%20parliament%2C%20political%20parties%2C%20for%20their%20part%2C%20need%20to%20secure%204%25%20of%20the%20vote.%C2%A0%20A%20preliminary%20result%20from%20the%20elections%20commission%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20announced%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20February%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20official%20outcome%20could%20take%20as%20long%20as%2035%20days%20to%20be%20made%20public%2C%20if%20no%20presidential%20contender%20gets%20over%2050%25%20of%20the%20votes%2C%20the%20contest%20goes%20to%20a%20second%20and%20final%20round%20between%20the%20top%20two%20in%20June.%20The%20new%20president%20will%20be%20sworn%20in%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKomnas%20HAM%2C%20an%20independent%20human%20rights%20body%2C%20said%20there%20are%2017%20groups%20of%20people%20who%20are%20likely%20to%20face%20challenges%20when%20exercising%20their%20right%20to%20vote.%20They%20include%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20LGBTQ%20communities%2C%20indigenous%20communities%20and%20religious%20minorities%2C%20among%20others.In%20North%20Sumatra%20province%2C%20Komnas%20HAM%20found%20instances%20of%20discrimination%20against%20LGBTQ%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20from%20the%20LGBTQ%20community%20felt%20increasingly%20insecure%20(to%20vote)%20because%20there%20was%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20regional%20leadership%20declaring%20Medan%20as%20an%20LGBTQ-free%20city%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pramono%20Ubaid%20Tanthowi%2C%20a%20Komnas%20HAM%20official%2C%20was%20quoted%20by%20local%20media%20outlet%20%3Cem%3Edetik.com%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20by%20people%20with%20disabilities%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20be%20low%2C%20said%20Kikin%20P.%20Tarigan%20of%20the%20Indonesian%20National%20Commission%20for%20Disabilities%2C%20pointing%20to%20inadequate%20efforts%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20election%20commission%20to%20register%20people%20with%20disabilities%20as%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findonesia-elections-what-you-need-to-know%2Fa-68230075%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3EDW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707806683000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112512%2Fimage-1825.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findonesia-elections-what-you-need-to-know%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Voters%20in%20the%20world's%20most%20populous%20Muslim-majority%20country%20will%20elect%20a%20new%20president%20and%20parliament%20on%20February%2014.%20It%20will%20mark%20the%20first%20change%20of%20leadership%20in%20a%20decade.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findonesia-elections-what-you-need-to-know%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Case%20for%20Bringing%20Paper%20Ballots%20Back%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F05084439%2F2022_12img04_Dec_2022_PTI12_04_.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EElectronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20have%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20public%20questioning%20for%20weeks%20now.%20People%20have%20argued%20for%20the%20return%20to%20paper%20ballots%2C%20as%20is%20the%20case%20in%20several%20global%20democracies.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPublic%20trust%20in%20EVMs%20has%20never%20been%20lower%20than%20it%20is%20today.%20This%20is%20because%20EVM%20voting%20does%20not%20comply%20with%20the%20essential%20principles%20of%20democracy%20that%20any%20electoral%20system%20should%20satisfy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20response%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20to%20this%20criticism%20is%20to%20hold%20roadshows%20%E2%80%9Cdemonstrating%E2%80%9D%20EVMs%20and%20naively%20bombarding%20the%20public%20with%20reams%20of%20%E2%80%98Frequently%20Asked%20Questions%20(FAQs)%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGlobally%2C%20there%20are%20five%20types%20of%20voting%20systems%20in%20use%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E1.%20Paper%20ballots%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E2.%20EVMs%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E3.%20EVMs%20with%20Voter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E4.%20Machine-readable%20paper%20ballots%2C%20and%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E5.%20Internet-based%20voting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20started%20with%20the%20first%20type%2C%20then%20went%20on%20to%20the%20second%20and%20is%20now%20using%20the%20third.%20While%20paper%20ballots%20comply%20with%20principles%20of%20democracy%2C%20EVMs%20do%20not.%20These%20principles%20are%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20voting%20process%20should%20be%20transparent%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20the%20general%20public%20should%20have%20the%20knowledge%20and%20satisfaction%20that%20their%20vote%20is%20correctly%20recorded%20and%20counted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20voting%20and%20counting%20process%20should%20be%20publicly%20auditable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EOrdinary%20citizens%20should%20be%20able%20to%20check%20the%20essential%20steps%20in%20the%20voting%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20should%20be%20examinability%20and%20verifiability%20of%20the%20voting%20process%2C%20counting%20of%20votes%20and%20ascertainment%20of%20the%20results.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20election%20process%20should%20not%20only%20be%20free%20and%20fair%2C%20but%20also%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20free%20and%20fair.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI%20should%20be%20in%20full%20control%20of%20the%20entire%20voting%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20can%20be%20better%20explained%20by%20comparing%20the%20process%20under%20the%20paper-ballot%20voting%20system%20and%20EVM%20voting.%20Let%20us%20do%20it%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20an%20ordinary%20voter%20who%20is%20transferring%20his%20sovereignty%20for%20five%20years%20to%20their%20elected%20representative.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdemocracy-voting-evm-vvpat-modi-election%5C%22%3EFrom%20the%20Will%20of%20the%20People%20to%20the%20Whim%20of%20the%20Machines%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProcess%20under%20the%20paper-ballot%20system%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EBallot-box%20is%20kept%20inside%20a%20secluded%20voting%20compartment%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EVoter%20enters%20the%20polling%20station%20and%2C%20after%20verification%2C%20is%20handed%20over%20the%20ballot-paper%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20examine%20it%20to%20check%20whether%20their%20candidate%20and%20the%20corresponding%20symbol%20is%20on%20the%20ballot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EVoter%20goes%20in%20to%20the%20voting%20compartment%20where%20the%20ballot-box%20is%20kept%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EVoter%20affixes%20the%20stamp%20on%20the%20candidate%2Fsymbol%20of%20their%20choice%20and%20puts%20it%20inside%20the%20ballot-box%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3ECounting%20is%20done%20manually%2C%20at%20the%20counting%20table%2C%20by%20physically%20sorting%20out%20the%20votes%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20Returning%20Officer%20(RO)%20and%20candidates%E2%80%99%20agents%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20counting%20table%20has%20one%20tray%20for%20each%20candidate%2C%20one%20for%20%E2%80%98doubtful%E2%80%99%20votes%20and%20one%20for%20%E2%80%98rejected%E2%80%99%20ones%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20part%20of%20verifying%2Fauditing%20process%2C%20votes%20are%20bundled%20(25%20each)%20and%20tallying%20is%20done%20between%20votes%20polled%20and%20votes%20to%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20are%20then%20counted%20by%20placing%20the%20votes%20in%20respective%20trays.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAgents%20keep%20a%20watch%20on%20each%20vote%20as%20it%20is%20placed%20in%20respective%20trays.%20Before%20the%20final%20tally%2C%20%E2%80%98Rejected%E2%80%99%20votes%20get%20re-confirmed%20and%20%E2%80%98doubtful%E2%80%99%20votes%20are%20reviewed%20with%20the%20agents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20disputes%20are%20resolved%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20if%20need%20be%2C%20with%20the%20intervention%20of%20the%20RO%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20paper%20ballot%20system%2C%20voters%20can%20check%20the%20accuracy%20of%20the%20ballot-paper%2C%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20name%20and%20verify%20whether%20it%20has%20been%20correctly%20marked.%20This%20provides%20knowledge%20and%20satisfaction%20that%20one%20has%20transferred%20the%20sovereignty%20to%20the%20candidate%20of%20their%20choice.%20In%20case%20of%20electoral%20dispute%2C%20physical%20reconstruction%20of%20the%20vote%20for%20authentication%20is%20possible.%20Vote%20counting%20is%20open%20and%20transparent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProcess%20under%20the%20electronic%20voting%20system%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EEVM%20comprises%20two%20units%20%E2%80%94%20a%20ballot%20unit%20(BU)%20containing%20the%20names%20of%20candidates%20and%20symbols%20against%20each%20button%20and%20a%20control%20unit%20(CU)%20containing%20the%20memory%20and%20display%20component%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20voter-verifiable%20paper%20audit%20trail%20(VVPAT)%20relates%20to%20the%20BU%20and%20the%20CU.%20The%20BU%2C%20CU%20and%20VVPAT%20are%20interconnected%20by%20an%20insulated%20cable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CU%20is%20with%20the%20polling%20officer%2C%20while%20the%20BU%20and%20VVPAT%20are%20placed%20inside%20the%20voting%20compartment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EEach%20time%20a%20voter%20enters%2C%20the%20polling%20officer%20presses%20the%20BU%20button.%20As%20the%20green%20light%20glows%2C%20it%20enables%20the%20voter%20to%20cast%20the%20vote%20by%20pressing%20the%20button%20on%20the%20BU%20against%20the%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20name%20and%20symbol.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EInstantly%2C%20the%20serial%20number%2C%20name%20and%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidate%20appears%20on%20the%20window%20of%20the%20VVPAT%2C%20remaining%20for%20about%20seven%20seconds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20seven%20seconds%2C%20a%20loud%20beep%20emanates%20from%20the%20CU%2C%20indicating%20the%20vote%20is%20cast.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20counting%20of%20votes%2C%20the%20counting%20official%20presses%20counting%20button%20on%20the%20CU%20that%20displays%20the%20number%20of%20votes%20polled%20against%20each%20candidate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20verification%2C%20auditing%20and%20dispute%20resolution%20on%20the%20spot%20before%20final%20results%20are%20announced.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftn-seshan-election-commissioner%5C%22%3ET.%20N.%20Seshan%2C%20the%20Unyielding%20Force%20That%20Cleansed%20India%E2%80%99s%20Elections%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAgainst%20absolute%20transparency%20of%20the%20paper-ballots%2C%20there%20is%20total%20opaqueness%20in%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20system.%20Everything%20is%20done%20inside%20a%20machine%2C%20in%20a%20non-transparent%20manner%2C%20without%20examination%2C%20knowledge%20and%20satisfaction%20as%20to%20whether%20sovereignty%20has%20been%20transferred%20to%20the%20candidate%20of%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20choice.%20All%20that%20the%20voter%20has%20is%20a%20chance%20to%20look%20at%20a%20slip%20for%20seven%20seconds.%20They%20have%20no%20assurance%20that%20the%20slip%20was%20counted%20or%20got%20manipulated%20between%20VVPAT%20and%20EVM.%20Under%20the%20EVM%20system%2C%20all%20that%20a%20voter%20does%20is%20to%20press%20a%20button%2C%20see%20a%20light%20and%20hear%20a%20sound.%20They%20have%20no%20idea%20whether%20the%20vote%20has%20been%20registered%20and%2C%20if%20so%2C%20to%20which%20candidate.%20There%20is%20no%20transparency%20even%20during%20counting%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExperts%20and%20professionals%20say%20that%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20claims%20of%20EVM%20(BU-VVPAT-CU)%20units%20being%20%E2%80%9Ctotally%20standalone%20machines%20having%20one-time%20programmable%20chips%E2%80%9D%20is%20not%20true.%20With%20the%20introduction%20of%20VVPATs%2C%20the%20name%20and%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidates%20will%20have%20to%20be%20uploaded%20to%20EVMs%20using%20an%20external%20device%20after%20the%20announcement%20of%20elections%20and%20finalisation%20of%20candidate%20list.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI%20Manual%20states%20that%20the%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Ltd.%20(BEL)%20and%20Electronics%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(ECIL)%20engineers%20are%20to%20use%20a%20device%20called%20Symbol%20Loading%20Unit%20(SLU)%20to%20electronically%20upload%20these%20details%20to%20the%20VVPAT.%20The%20same%20manual%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20these%20devices%20need%20not%20be%20stored%20in%20the%20strong%20room%20along%20with%20EVM%2FVVPATs%20and%20are%20to%20be%20released%20to%20the%20engineers%20immediately%20after%20the%20poll%C2%A0%20%E2%80%93%20thus%20leaving%20them%20outside%20of%20the%20custody%20chain%20of%20ROs.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20wired%20connection%20of%20EVM%2FVVPATs%20to%20an%20external%20device%20not%20maintained%20within%20the%20RO%2FDistrict%20Election%20Officers%20after%20the%20elections%20are%20announced%2C%20candidate%20sequence%20is%20firmed%20up%2C%20and%20second%20randomisation%20and%20booth%20allotment%20of%20EVMs%20finalised%2C%C2%A0%20makes%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20practices%20in%20conducting%20elections%20extremely%20suspect.%20This%20has%20exposed%20the%20voting%20and%20counting%20to%20manipulation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERule%2056(D)(4)(b)%20of%20Conduct%20of%20Election%20Rules%2C%201961%2C%20provides%20that%20the%20count%20of%20VVPATs%20shall%20prevail%20over%20the%20count%20reflected%20in%20EVMs%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20discrepancy%20between%20the%20votes%20displayed%20on%20the%20control%20unit%20and%20the%20counting%20of%20the%20paper%20slips%2C%20amend%20the%20result%20sheet%20in%20Form%2020%20as%20per%20the%20paper%20slips%20count.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20rule%20is%20a%20statutory%20admission%20of%20the%20position%20in%20law%20and%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20finally%20the%20VVPAT%20which%20accurately%20captures%20the%20will%20of%20the%20voter%20and%20that%20variance%20or%20errors%20in%20the%20results%20captured%20in%20the%20EVMs%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out%20for%20any%20given%20reason.%20Given%20the%20statutory%20acknowledgement%2C%20it%20is%20manifestly%20arbitrary%20and%20in%20violation%20of%20Article%2014%20to%20not%20to%20fully%20count%20the%20VVPAT%20slips%20before%20the%20results%20are%20declared.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EECI%20has%20lost%20control%20under%20the%20electronic%20system%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20ballot%20paper%20system%2C%20ECI%20had%20full%20control%20and%20supervision%20over%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20ballot-boxes%2C%20printing%20of%20ballot-papers%2C%20its%20despatch%20and%20counting%20of%20votes.%20That%20is%20not%20the%20case%20with%20EVMs%20that%20contains%20two%20EEPROMS%20(Electrically%20Erasable%20and%20Programmable%20Memory)%20inside%20the%20control%20unit%20in%20which%20the%20voting%20data%20is%20stored.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBEL%20and%20ECIL%2C%20manufacturers%20of%20EVMs%2C%20are%20not%20under%20the%20control%20or%20supervision%20of%20ECI.%20They%20are%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20respective%20ministries%C2%A0%20and%20the%20day-to-day%20administration%20is%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20packed%20with%20ruling%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20functionaries.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20entities%20share%20the%20confidential%20software%20programme%20with%20foreign%20chip%20manufacturers%20to%20copy%20it%20on%20to%20micro-controllers%20used%20in%20the%20EVMs.%20When%20these%20foreign%20companies%20deliver%20micro-controllers%20fused%20with%20software%20code%20to%20the%20EVM%20manufacturers%2C%20neither%20the%20manufacturer%20nor%20the%20ECI%20officials%20can%20read%20back%20their%20contents%20because%20they%20are%20locked.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20clear%2C%20therefore%2C%20that%20EVM%20voting%20does%20not%20comply%20with%20any%20of%20the%20principles%20of%20democracy%20that%20are%20paramount%20which%20makes%20it%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20imperative%20for%20India%20to%20return%20to%20the%20paper%20ballot.%20The%20only%20grievance%20against%20this%20system%20is%20that%20there%20used%20to%20be%20booth%20capturing%20and%20ballot-stuffing.%20This%20was%20when%20the%20supervision%2C%20security%2C%20transportation%20and%20communication%20systems%20were%20primitive%20%E2%80%93%20not%20the%20case%20any%20longer.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20senior%20election%20officials%2C%20ECI%20observers%2C%20police%20and%20flying%20squads%20can%20observe%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20polling%20booths%20live%20through%20CCTV%20cameras%20and%20can%20intervene%20instantly%20in%20the%20event%20of%20any%20mischief.%20Besides%2C%20sensitive%20booths%20are%20guarded%20by%20armed%20police%20with%20orders%20to%20shoot%20in%20case%20of%20any%20booth%20capturing%20and%20ballot%20stuffing.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20reason%20for%20the%20ECI%20not%20to%20comply%20with%20this%20demand.%20Any%20amendment%20to%20election%20law%20can%20be%20notified%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes%20through%20ordinance.%20Logistics%20of%20procuring%20ballot%20boxes%20and%20other%20material%20could%20be%20done%20in%20couple%20of%20weeks%20because%20they%20are%20being%20used%20for%20panchayat%20and%20local%20bodies%20elections%20and%20are%20continuously%20being%20manufactured.%20Trained%20personnel%20are%20also%20available.%20Ballot%20papers%20will%2C%20in%20any%20case%2C%20be%20printed%20only%20after%20the%20candidate%20list%20is%20finalised.%20All%20that%20is%20needed%20is%20to%20shortlist%20printing%20presses%20and%20have%20them%20cleared%20after%20security%20checks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20without%20playing%20%E2%80%98marketing%20agents%E2%80%99%20for%20EVMs%2C%20ECI%20should%20heed%20the%20cry%20of%20the%20people%20and%20return%20to%20paper%20ballots%20to%20save%20democracy%20.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EM.G.%20Devasahayam%20is%20former%20Army%20and%20IAS%20Officer.%20He%20is%20Coordinator%20of%20Citizens%20Commission%20on%20Elections%20and%20editor%20of%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EElectoral%20Democracy%E2%80%94An%20Inquiry%20into%20the%20Fairness%20and%20Integrity%20of%20Elections%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707806138000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F05084439%2F2022_12img04_Dec_2022_PTI12_04_.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-case-for-bringing-paper-ballots-back%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Public%20trust%20in%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20has%20never%20been%20lower%20than%20it%20is%20today%20and%20there's%20a%20good%20reason%20why.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-case-for-bringing-paper-ballots-back%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Systemic%20Sexual%20Assault%2C%20an%20Oppressive%20TMC%20and%20Not%20Much%20Recourse%3A%20What%20Sandeshkhali%20Villagers%20Say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112718%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.25.26-AM-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESandeshkhali%20(Bengali)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Since%20last%20week%2C%20extraordinary%20sights%20of%20protest%20and%20political%20developments%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20a%20village%20in%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20North%2024%20Parganas%20that%20had%20largely%20been%20out%20of%20the%20radar%20until%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-bengals-sandeshkhali-controversial-tmc-leader-sheikh-shahjahans-hold-is-powerful%5C%22%3Enews%20of%20an%20attack%20on%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20officials%20by%20a%20local%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%3C%2Fa%3E%20broke%20last%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20protests%20that%20have%20taken%20place%20since%20February%208%20are%20not%20directly%20linked%20to%20the%20tussle%20between%20state%20and%20Union%20government.%20Instead%2C%20they%20concern%20hundreds%20women%20who%20have%20alleged%20that%20top%20TMC%20leaders%20in%20the%20area%20have%20unleashed%20a%20%E2%80%98reign%20of%20terror%E2%80%99%20including%20consistent%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20sexual%20assault%20against%20local%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20women%20have%20named%20TMC%20strongman%20Shahjahan%20Sheikh%20%E2%80%93%20who%20is%20incidentally%20absconding%20since%20the%20ED%20visit%20%E2%80%93%20and%20his%20aides%20Sibaprasad%20alias%20Sibu%20Hazra%2C%20and%20Uttam%20Sardar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20many%20women%20have%20spoken%20to%20various%20reporters%20and%20described%20instances%20of%20alleged%20sexual%20assault%20by%20TMC%20leaders.%20Some%20have%20set%20fire%20to%20properties%20belonging%20to%20TMC%20leaders.%20Police%20have%20largely%20not%20intervened%2C%20however%2C%20internet%20has%20been%20shutdown%20and%20Section%20144%20has%20been%20imposed%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20cable%20operators%20have%20been%20instructed%20to%20pause%20services%20there.%20The%20area%20office%20of%20the%20TMC%20is%20under%20lock%20and%20key.%20Police%20are%20stationed%20at%20regular%20intervals%20throughout%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20reporter%20saw%20police%20give%20chase%20to%20a%20woman%20when%20a%20few%20villagers%20intervened%20and%20escorted%20her%20to%20safety.%20According%20to%20locals%2C%20she%20had%20been%20a%20prominent%20figure%20in%20the%20ongoing%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13113022%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.28.17-AM-e1707804265919.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13113022%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.28.17-AM-e1707804265919.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13113022%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.28.17-AM-e1707804265919-300x175.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13113022%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.28.17-AM-e1707804265919-1024x598.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696876%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22631%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWomen%20protesting%20at%20Sandeshkhali.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAllegations%20of%20horrific%20crimes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20two%20women%20who%20recounted%20horrific%20abuse.%20Both%20have%20asked%20for%20their%20names%20to%20be%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20brought%20me%20into%20the%20party%20office%2C%20where%20a%20group%2