%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112610%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.25.28-AM-724x1024.jpeg%20724w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696871%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22418%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20poster%20%E2%80%98welcoming%E2%80%99%20Shahjahan.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShahjahan%20Sheikh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20local%20said%20that%20rising%20awareness%20of%20how%20the%20state%20government%20is%20%E2%80%9Clooting%E2%80%9D%20people%E2%80%99s%20money%20is%20why%20internet%20has%20been%20shut%20down.%20%E2%80%9CYouth%20are%20able%20to%20look%20up%20how%20%3Cspan%3E%20Shahjahan%20Sheikh%20has%20claimed%20to%20have%20done%20work%20worth%20crores%20which%20have%20come%20to%20naught%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShahjahan%20Sheikh%20is%20very%20much%20the%20centre%20of%20all%20things%20Sandeshkhali.%20It%20is%20to%20search%20his%20house%20that%20ED%20officials%20arrived%20in%20the%20village%20in%20January%20this%20year%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20public%20distribution%20system%20scam.%C2%A0%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20Shahjahan%E2%80%99s%20whereabouts%20have%20remained%20unknown%20despite%20multiple%20summons%20and%20a%20lookout%20notice%20by%20the%20ED.%20His%20legal%20team%20has%20sought%20court%20approval%20for%20bail%20on%20several%20occasions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDidi%20is%20protecting%20him.%20He%20is%20being%20sheltered%20by%20the%20police%20and%20the%20administration.%20They%20might%20want%20to%20diffuse%20the%20anger%20by%20arresting%20one%20or%20two%20people%2C%20but%20the%20main%20culprit%20is%20still%20at%20large%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20local%20woman%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Kacharipara%20part%20of%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20another%20villager%20says%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Efinancial%20corruption%20in%20the%20village%20%E2%80%9Cstarted%20soon%20after%20Trinamool%20came%20to%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYoung%20boys%20of%2015-16%20years%20were%20lured%20with%20alcohol.%20The%20biker%20gang%20of%20the%20party%20picked%20up%20our%20children%20from%20school%2C%20gave%20them%20guns%2C%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20take%20part%20in%20violence.%20The%20situation%20has%20worsened%20since%202018.%20They%20looted%20money%2C%20land%20and%20our%20women%E2%80%99s%20honour%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20villager%20claimed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolice%3A%20Arrests%2C%20re-arrests%20and%20no%20%E2%80%98rape%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20three%20being%20accused%20of%20such%20crimes%20%E2%80%93%20Shahjahan%2C%20Uttam%20Sardar%20and%20Sibu%20Hazra%20%E2%80%93%20are%20members%20of%20the%20TMC-run%20Zilla%20Parishad.%20While%20Uttam%20won%20uncontested%2C%20Shahjahan%20and%20Sibu%20received%2099.9%25%20and%2098%25%20of%20total%20votes%20in%20the%20latest%20panchayat%20polls.%20Many%20believe%20that%20such%20figures%20indicate%20irregularities%20in%20the%20voting%20process%20rather%20than%20the%20mass%20support%20they%20command.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFaced%20with%20massive%20outrage%20from%20across%20the%20state%2C%20TMC%20on%20February%2010%20suspended%20Uttam%20for%20six%20years.%20For%20locals%2C%20this%20is%20little%20more%20than%20a%20token%20gesture.%20While%20Uttam%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20soon%20after%20that%2C%20police%20also%20arrested%20former%20Sandeshkhali%20MLA%20and%20CPI(M)%20state%20committee%20member%20Nirapada%20Sardar%20on%20the%20afternoon%20of%20February%2011%2C%20from%20Kolkata%2C%20based%20on%20an%20FIR%20filed%20by%20Sibu%20who%20is%20still%20absconding.%20In%20the%20mean%20time%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20Bikash%20Sinha%20was%20also%20held.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20were%20produced%20in%20the%20Basirhat%20court%20a%20day%20ago.%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20Uttam%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Bikash%20got%20bail%2C%20but%20CPI(M)%20leader%20Nirapada%2C%20did%20not.%C2%A0%20BJP%20and%20TMC%20workers%C2%A0%20outside%20the%20court%20welcomed%20the%20two%20amidst%20much%20fanfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20afterwards%2C%20police%20re-arrested%20Sinha%20over%20what%20they%20said%20was%20%E2%80%9Can%20old%20case%E2%80%9D.%20When%20protests%20led%20by%20local%20BJP%20workers%20appeared%20to%20go%20out%20of%20hand%2C%20and%20in%20dramatic%20scenes%2C%20Uttam%20was%20then%20brought%20back%20and%20re-arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20constituted%20a%2010-member%20team%20to%20be%20headed%20by%20a%20DIG-rank%20woman%20IPS%20officer%20to%20look%20into%20the%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20assault.%20The%20team%20will%20begin%20groundwork%20from%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Barasat%20Range%20DIG%20Sumit%20Kumar%20told%20reporters%20that%20four%20complaints%20have%20yet%20been%20filed%20at%20Sandeshkhali.%20%E2%80%9CNone%20of%20them%20mention%20rape.%20If%20we%20get%20such%20a%20complaint%2C%20we%20will%20take%20action.%20We%20are%20investigating%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20to%20respond%20to%20this%20claim%2C%20a%20woman%20who%20had%20spoken%20to%20The%20Wire%20of%20sexual%20assault%20said%20that%20she%20had%20grown%20so%20used%20to%20seeing%20policemen%20in%20public%20places%20with%20the%20accused%20TMC%20leaders%20that%20she%20does%20not%20expect%20behaviour%20to%20the%20contrary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20police%20have%20also%20allegedly%20stopped%20groups%20led%20by%20opposition%20leaders%20to%20the%20village%2C%20although%20the%20governor%2C%20C.V.%20Ananda%20Bose%20has%20visited%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Wire%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Basirhat%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Dr.%20Hossain%20Mehedi%20Rehman%2C%20requesting%20various%20details%20on%20what%20the%20arrests%20and%20re-arrests%20were%20on%20the%20basis%20of%2C%20and%20on%20the%20lack%20of%20police%20action%20initially.%20This%20report%20will%20be%20updated%20once%20there%20is%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13111627%2FUntitled-design-11.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13111627%2FUntitled-design-11.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13111627%2FUntitled-design-11-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13111627%2FUntitled-design-11-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696864%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20boy%20(face%20blurred%20to%20protect%20identity%20as%20he%20is%20a%20minor)%20points%20to%20a%20fishery%20created%20allegedly%20after%20illegally%20occupying%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20land%2C%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20land%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2011%2C%20as%20this%20reporter%20chatted%20with%20residents%20on%20Khulna%20Island%2C%20some%20men%20on%20bikes%20suddenly%20appeared%20to%20be%20patrolling%20the%20area.%20A%20few%20villagers%20grew%20alert.%20One%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CBe%20careful.%20Parimal%20Mridha%20and%20Santosh%20have%20heard%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20talking%20to%20you.%20They%20might%20torture%20us%20again.%E2%80%9D%20Both%20are%20local%20TMC%20leaders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVillagers%20pointed%20to%20a%20massive%20fishery.%20Once%20known%20as%20Majherpara%2C%20the%20land%20which%20used%20to%20yield%20crops%20twice%20a%20year%2C%20stands%20barren%20today.%20Three%20years%20ago%2C%20they%20said%2C%20