in%2Fcrime%2Findian-army-torture-jammu-and-kashmir-poonch-bjp-gujjar-bakkerwal%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHigher%20authorities%2C%20at%20least%20publicly%2C%20seem%20to%20be%20going%20out%20of%20their%20way%20to%20heal%20wounds%20in%20Topa%20Peer.%20Clearly%2C%20they%20have%20not%20taken%20this%20event%20lightly.%20On%2025%20December%2C%20Manoj%20Pande%2C%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20visited%20Jammu%2C%20though%20he%20reportedly%20only%20looked%20into%20the%20prevailing%20security%20situation%20in%20the%20region.%20Two%20days%20later%2C%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20defence%20minister%2C%20visited%20Rajouri.%20He%20had%20flowery%20words%20for%20the%20troops%20on%20the%20occasion%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20aim%20to%20eliminate%20the%20terrorists%2C%20our%20aim%20should%20be%20bigger%3B%20we%20have%20to%20win%20the%20hearts%20of%20our%20countrymen.%E2%80%9D%20He%20went%20on%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20incidents%20of%2022%20December%2C%20but%20merely%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmistake%E2%80%9D%20that%20may%20hurt%20the%20citizens%20of%20the%20country.%20Days%20later%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20also%20chaired%20a%20security%20review%20meeting%20on%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20reportedly%20attended%20by%20the%20chiefs%20of%20the%20IB%2C%20the%20army%2C%20the%20police%2C%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20and%20the%20Research%20and%20Analysis%20Wing%E2%80%94India%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20intelligence%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20Topa%20Peer%2C%20though%2C%20the%20army%20seemed%20to%20be%20in%20overdrive.%20In%20early%20January%2C%20the%20army%20accelerated%20Operation%20Sadbhavana%E2%80%94a%20counter-insurgency%20mission%20that%20involved%20building%20schools%20and%20distributing%20free%20food%20to%20civilians%2C%20aimed%20at%20winning%20%E2%80%9Chearts%20and%20minds.%E2%80%9D%20They%20refurbished%20a%20government%20dispensary%2C%20and%20distributed%20notebooks%20and%20pencils%20to%20children.%20Most%20notably%2C%20locals%20told%20me%2C%20the%20army%20had%20begun%20work%20on%20building%20a%20road%20to%20the%20village%2C%20with%20earth%20movers%20already%20rolling%20in%20to%20cut%20down%20the%20forests%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20families%20of%20those%20who%20had%20died%20on%2022%20December%20were%20not%20moved.%20Speaking%20about%20the%20new%20solar%20lights%20that%20had%20been%20set%20up%20across%20the%20village%20under%20Operation%20Sadbhavana%2C%20Lal%E2%80%99s%20daughter-in-law%2C%20Rangeela%20Begum%2C%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20blacked%20out%20our%20lives%20and%20are%20now%20installing%20solar%20lights%20%E2%80%A6%20this%20is%20no%20substitute%20for%20justice.%20It%E2%80%99s%20just%20hooliganism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20affected%20families%2C%20the%20bundles%20of%20cash%20they%20received%E2%80%94Rs%2010%20lakh%20for%20the%20dead%20and%20lesser%20for%20the%20injured%E2%80%94were%20expected%20to%20replace%20their%20loved%20ones.%20Nazir%2C%20Shaukat%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20was%20visited%20by%20the%20commanding%20officer%20of%20the%2016%20RR%20and%20a%20brigadier%2C%20who%20handed%20him%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%20Vali%20was%20given%20the%20same%20amount.%20He%20told%20me%20he%20did%20not%20know%20what%20to%20do%20with%20it.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20labourers%20and%20I%20have%20worked%20my%20whole%20life%20with%20the%20border%20roads%20organisation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%20raised%20my%20children%20in%20extreme%20poverty%20and%20hoped%20one%20day%20they%20will%20take%20care%20of%20me%20when%20I%20get%20old.%E2%80%9D%20The%20money%20would%20do%20little%20to%20help.%20Farooq%20got%20Rs%202.3%20lakh%2C%20while%20Irfaan%20got%20Rs%201.5%20lakh.%20Fazal%20was%20given%20Rs%202.5%20lakh.%20Now%20barely%20able%20to%20walk%2C%20he%20told%20me%20the%20money%20was%20meaningless.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20five%20kids%20and%20a%20family%20of%20seven%20to%20support.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20myself%20being%20able%20to%20work%20ever%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20427px)%2085vw%2C%20427px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13105337%2FTC.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22427%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13105337%2FTC.jpeg%20677w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13105337%2FTC-226x300.jpeg%20226w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696854%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22568%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20families%20of%20those%20who%20were%20tortured%20and%20murdered%20on%2022%20December%20got%20money%20from%20the%20army%20to%20pressure%20them%20into%20not%20pursuing%20legal%20cases.%20This%20blood%20money%20was%20likely%20rerouted%20military%20intelligence%20funds.%20Photo%3A%20Jatinder%20Kaur%20Tur%20for%20The%20Caravan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20serving%20and%20retired%20army%20officers%20told%20me%20that%20this%20money%20likely%20came%20from%20military%20intelligence%20funds%2C%20which%20are%20usually%20unaccounted%20for.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20cases%20of%20army%20trying%20to%20compensate%20an%20illegal%20act%20or%20a%20crime%20committed%20by%20its%20men%20is%20not%20new%2C%20though%20the%20money%20is%20meant%20for%20various%20operations%20and%20the%20connected%20requirements%2C%20including%20rewarding%20informers%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20serving%20army%20officer%20told%20me.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20used%20to%20be%20covert%20%E2%80%A6%20in%20private%2C%20not%20so%20blatant%20and%20overt.%E2%80%9D%20A%20retired%20senior%20army%20officer%20told%20me%20that%20such%20a%20blatant%20display%20of%20money%2C%20without%20any%20exemplary%20justice%20and%20restoration%20of%20the%20faith%20of%20those%20affected%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Cworse%20than%20blood%20money.%E2%80%9D%20The%20notes%20the%20affected%20families%20showed%20me%20were%20fresh%2C%20still%20wrapped%20in%20the%20plastic%20of%20the%20currency%20mints%20of%20Nashik%20and%20Dewas%2C%20even%20showing%20their%20recent%20date%20of%20manufacture.%20Two%20Indian%20Revenue%20Service%20officers%20told%20me%20that%20this%20could%20mean%20that%20these%20notes%20came%20directly%20from%20the%20mint%20and%20that%20even%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20might%20not%20be%20aware%20of%20this%20leakage%20of%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20state%20governments%20often%20give%20solatia%20for%20families%20of%20those%20who%20suffered%20in%20a%20disaster%2C%20the%20army%20itself%20publicly%20handing%20out%20money%20is%20likely%20unprecedented%2C%20even%20in%20a%20region%20where%20it%20has%20engineered%20its%20fair%20share%20of%20disasters.%20Multiple%20locals%2C%20including%20village%20chiefs%2C%20told%20me%20that%20the%20cash%20was%20the%20symbol%20of%20a%20compromise%2C%20so%20the%20families%20would%20not%20pursue%20the%20case.%20But%2C%20in%20a%20court%20of%20law%2C%20compromises%20can%20only%20be%20reached%20between%20equal%20parties.%20Rangeela%20Begum%20told%20me%20that%20there%20can%20never%20be%20a%20provision%20of%20compromise%20or%20compensation%20when%20there%20are%20unequal%20parties%20involved.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20might%20be%20poor%20but%20we%20still%20want%20justice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMassacres%20are%20not%20rare%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20From%20the%20Jammu%20massacres%20of%201947%20to%20the%20Gawkadal%2C%20Handwara%2C%20Zakoora%2C%20Hawal%2C%20Bijbehera%2C%20Sopore%20and%20Kupwara%20massacres%20in%20the%201990s%20alone%2C%20they%20have%20a%20long%20history.%20Custodial%20torture%2C%20killings%20and%20staged%20encounters%20are%20commoner%20still.%20The%20way%20the%20Indian%20state%20has%20often%20dealt%20with%20extrajudicial%20violence%20is%20by%20further%20clampdowns%2C%20shutting%20off%20the%20internet%2C%20announcing%20curfews%20and%20flooding%20in%20more%20troops.%20In%20that%20sense%2C%20the%20response%20to%20the%2022%20December%20case%20is%20a%20break%20in%20the%20pattern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20break%20is%20likely%20because%20of%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20victims%2C%20all%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakkerwals.%20Not%20only%20are%20the%20communities%20crucial%20for%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20function%20in%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20and%20an%20indispensable%20source%20of%20intelligence%2C%20they%20also%20play%20vitally%20into%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20hope%20for%20the%20region.%20The%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakkerwals%20are%20together%20the%20third%20largest%20ethnic%20group%20in%20the%20union%20territory.%20Since%202020%2C%20a%20three-member%20delimitation%20commission%20has%20been%20working%20to%20redistrict%20the%20region%2C%20its%20latest%20report%20adding%20seats%20to%20the%20Hindu-majority%20Jammu%20region%20to%20accord%20it%20nearly%20the%20same%20electoral%20weight%20as%20the%20Muslim-majority%20Kashmir%20Valley.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindu-majoritarian%20impulses%20for%20the%20region%20cannot%20succeed%20without%20preserving%20its%20tenuous%20but%20still%20existent%20relationship%20with%20the%20Gujjar%20and%20Bakkerwal%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20last%20few%20elections%20the%20BJP%20realised%20that%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20breach%20Pir%20Panjal%20electorally%20because%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20population%20are%20Muslim%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bilal%20Rashid%2C%20a%20Congress%20leader%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20told%20me.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20some%20newly%20reserved%20seats%20in%20this%20region%20the%20Gujjar-Bakerwals%20are%20around%2040%20to%2045%20percent%20of%20the%20electorate%20and%20decide%20outcomes.%20They%20also%20have%20a%20significant%20presence%20in%20other%20constituencies.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%20that%20the%20communities%20are%2C%20%E2%80%9Cpatriotic%20and%20because%20of%20this%20politics%20they%20are%20finding%20it%20tough%20to%20work%20along%20the%20border%2C%E2%80%9D%20especially%20now%20with%20an%20increase%20in%20militancy%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20centrality%20of%20the%20community%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20plans%20means%20that%20an%20increasingly%20politicised%20army%2C%20too%2C%20needs%20to%20react%20differently%20than%20how%20it%20may%20have%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20suggestions%20seem%20to%20be%20only%20paper%20thin.%20Two%20senior%20army%20officials%20told%20me%20that%20while%20the%20army%20was%20advertising%20its%20new%20Sadbhavana%20drive%20in%20Poonch%2C%20Lieutenant%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20Northern%20Command%2C%20sent%20out%20directions%20to%20be%20complied%20by%20all%20ranks%20below%20him.%20These%20are%20ominous%20directions%2C%20which%20suggests%20that%20little%20will%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20directions%20note%20that%20the%20army%20should%20identify%20%E2%80%9Cblack%2C%20grey%20and%20white%20villages%20and%20population%E2%80%94treat%20accordingly.%E2%80%9D%20This%20suggests%20a%20continued%20policy%20of%20collective%20punishment%20in%20the%20region.%20It%20also%20added%20that%20the%20aura%20of%20the%20army%20must%20be%20felt.%20Oddly%2C%20the%20army%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20aim%20at%20stamping%20out%20militancy%20in%20the%20region%2C%20instead%20noting%20that%20the%20southern%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%2C%20can%20have%20an%20acceptable%20figure%20of%20around%20thirty%20militants.%20The%20directions%20seemingly%20contain%20instructions%20from%20Amit%20Shah%20that%20the%20army%20will%20be%20an%20umbrella%20organisation%20and%20that%20the%20army%20has%20to%20play%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20the%20entire%20process%2C%20including%20initiatives%20of%20development%20programmes.%20It%20concludes%20with%20a%20single%20point%3A%20%E2%80%9CAggressive%20outlook.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20469px)%2085vw%2C%20469px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2F