%20exact%20same%20training%20of%20one%20year%20along%20with%20male%20cadets.%20We%20never%20took%20help%20from%20anyone%20in%20doing%20our%20duty%20or%20task%2C%20be%20it%20night%20guard%20patrol%20check%20duty%20or%20any%20other%20professional%20task.%20My%20trainer%20said%20no%20one%20should%20be%20able%20to%20say%20that%20we%20were%20less%20than%20any%20male%20counterpart.%20And%20I%20ensured%20that%20no%20one%20could%20point%20out%20anything%20just%20because%20I%20am%20a%20female.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%20individual%20officers%20are%20good%20but%20female%20officers%20in%20general%20were%20treated%20like%20guinea%20pigs%20%E2%80%93%20experimented%20on%20and%20then%20thrown%20away.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20IAF%20and%20serve%20for%20more%20years%2C%20just%20like%20my%20male%20counterparts%2C%20but%20we%20weren%E2%80%99t%20allowed%20to%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20with%20a%20sigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20raise%20this%20issue%2C%2032%20female%20officers%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20court%20and%20in%202003%2C%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20(PIL)%20was%20instituted%20before%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20titled%20%E2%80%98Babita%20Puniya%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20permanent%20commission%20to%20women%20SSC%20Officers%E2%80%99%2C%20highlighting%20the%20gender%20discrimination%20being%20meted%20out%20to%20women%20officers%20in%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAfter%20years%20of%20struggle%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20stated%20that%20the%20Permanent%20Commission%20shall%20be%20offered%20to%20women%20officers%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20five%20years%2C%20subject%20to%20vacancies%20and%20suitability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20judgment%20was%20said%20to%20be%20implemented%20by%20the%20IAF%20for%20only%20those%20officers%20who%20were%20in%20service%20or%20those%20retired%2Freleased%20officers%20who%20were%20not%2