s%20being%20wasted.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20discovered%20a%20community%20of%20bamboo%20artisans%20whose%20craft%20was%20fading%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Kotwaliyas%20in%20the%20region%20are%20renowned%20for%20their%20skill%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20their%20art%20was%20being%20neglected%20and%20dying%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20also%20began%20educating%20his%20students%20about%20the%20benefits%20of%20using%20Bambusa%20bamboo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20was%20in%20the%20process%20of%20educating%20more%20people%20and%20reaching%20out%20to%20craftsmen%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20disrupting%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20period%2C%20Ankit%20encountered%20craftsmen%20suffering%20due%20to%20the%20decline%20in%20tourism.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learned%20that%20the%20younger%20generations%20of%20these%20craftsmen%20were%20reluctant%20to%20continue%20the%20tradition%20as%20they%20saw%20no%20future%20in%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Ankit%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20immense%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334214%2Fmaharashtra-tetwali-village-namita-namdev-bhurkood-bamboo-kandils-trains-tribal-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epotential%20of%20bamboo%3C%2Fa%3E%20became%20crucial.%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20them%20to%20abandon%20their%20craft%20and%20migrate%20to%20cities%20in%20search%20of%20jobs.%20So%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20create%20daily-use%20furniture%20with%20modern%20designs%20to%20appeal%20to%20urban%20consumers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Ankit%2C%20along%20with%20a%20few%20students%20and%20four%20local%20craftsmen%2C%20embarked%20on%20creating%20sustainable%20yet%20modern%20designs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESturdy%2C%20Sustainable%20and%20Modern%