3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20makes%20this%20device%20so%20affordable%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Satyam%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20cost%20reduction%20of%20our%20device%20to%20Rs%2012%2C000%20is%20a%20significant%20achievement%20when%20compared%20to%20similar%20products%20from%20international%20companies%20like%20YSI%2C%20Hanna%2C%20and%20WTW%2C%20which%20are%20priced%20between%20Rs%2097%2C000%20and%20Rs%202%2C63%2C000.%20The%20high%20costs%20of%20these%20competing%20products%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20factors%20such%20as%20import%20duties%2C%20limited%20after-sales%20support%2C%20and%20high%20operational%20expenses%20as%20these%20products%20are%20not%20made%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20approach%20to%20bringing%20down%20costs%20involved%20using%20industrial-grade%20water%20sensors%20and%20leveraging%20Google%E2%80%99s%20free%20web%20hosting%20and%20real-time%20database%20services.%20This%20strategic%20choice%20not%20only%20made%20our%20device%20affordable%20but%20also%20integrated%20it%20with%20cutting-edge%20IoT%20capabilities.%20We%20developed%20this%20product%20in-house%20at%20the%20Enzyme%20and%20Microbial%20Technology%20Lab%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChallenges%20in%20developing%20the%20device%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20initial%20stages%20of%20development%2C%20Satyam%2C%20his%20mentor%20and%20colleagues%20encountered%20challenges%20related%20to%20power%20distribution%2C%20weight%20balancing%2C%20and%20maintaining%20a%20compact%20design.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20these%20issues%2C%20they%20made%20several%20adjustments%2C%20including%20redesigning%20the%20case%20and%20the%20outer%20structure%20to%20improve%20buoyancy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20integrated%20a%2020%2C000%20mAh%20high%20endurance%20battery%20to%20ensure%20longer%20operational%20times%20when%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F294472%2Fair-conditioner-ac-works-on-solar-panel-energy-reduce-electricity-bill%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20power%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20not%20in%20use.%20Further%20refinements%20were%20made%20to%20enhance%20the%20smooth%20processing%20and%20display%20of%20data%2C%20ultimately%20overcoming%20the%20initial%20challenges%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20from%20concept%20to%20the%20current%20prototype%20spanned%20four%20years.%20Through%20successive%20iterations%2C%20they%20have%20refined%20the%20device%2C%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20monitored%20water%20parameters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20current%20model%20represents%20the%20third%20prototype%20with%20plans%20to%20expand%20its%20capabilities%20further%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-IoT-Feature-1707316244.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IoT-enabled%20water%20quality%20measuring%20device%20in%20IIT-Guwahati%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-IoT-Feature-1707316244.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-IoT-Feature-1707316244-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-IoT-Feature-1707316244-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-IoT-Feature-1707316244-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads