-2-1707304736.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleap-2-1707304736-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleap-2-1707304736-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleap-2-1707304736-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleap-2-1707304736-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleap-2-1707304736-150x100.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleap-2-1707304736-272x182.jpg%20272w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340984%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20device%20takes%20up%204%20feet%20x%202%20feet%20space%2C%20which%20is%20equivalent%20to%20a%20vertically%20wall-mounted%2055-inch%20LED%20TV.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAman%20Rai%2C%20a%20chemical%20engineering%20graduate%20from%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%20is%20a%20passionate%20runner%20with%20many%20ultra-marathons%20under%20his%20belt.%20Upon%20starting%20his%20career%2C%20he%20struggled%20to%20juggle%20his%20job%20responsibilities%20with%20regular%20gym%20visits%20for%20strength%20training%2C%20which%20is%20essential%20for%20runners.%20Residing%20in%20a%20rented%20accommodation%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20limited%20equipment%20at%20his%20disposal%20at%20home%20fell%20short%20of%20adequately%20supporting%20his%20training%20regimen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnurag%20Dani%20also%20found%20it%20tough%20to%20find%20time%20to%20head%20to%20the%20gym%20due%20to%20long%20work%20hours.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Rohit%20Patel%20and%20Amal%20George%2C%20who%20were%20studying%20robotics%2C%20spent%20hours%20building%20solutions%20for%20everyday%20problems%2C%20and%20were%20keen%20on%20solving%20this%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20really%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founders%2C%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20was%20no%20single%20equipment%20that%20could%20replicate%20the%20entire%20gym%20at%20home.%20They%20discovered%20that%20home%20gym%20equipment%20was%20big%2C%20costly%2C%20and%20demanded%20ample%20space.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20struggled%20to%20accurately%20monitor%20their%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20have%20to%20keep%20buying%20different%20weights%20and%20bars%20to%20train%20at%20home.%20This%20occupies%20a%20lot%20of%20space%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%2C%20especially%20in%20rented%20spaces%20and%20small%20apartments.%20It%20also%20becomes%20bulky%20and%20unsafe.%20So%20we%20decided%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aman%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20a%20new%20digital-weights%20technology%20emerged.%20Amal%20and%20Rohit%2C%20robotics%20graduates%2C%20explored%20creating%20a%20similar%20system.%20They%20began%20prototyping%2C%20aiming%20to%20replace%20physical%20weights%20with%20digital%20ones%20using%20motors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20tried%20to%20replicate%20the%20same%20types%20of%20resistance%20that%20a%20physical%20weight%20provides%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20motor%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Aman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20the%20four%20of%20them%20worked%20on%20building%20prototypes%2C%20investing%20almost%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20of%20their%20own%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Aroleap%20X%20comes%20with%20over%20150%20exercises%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FAroleapp-1707304740.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%