E2%80%9CThe%20technology%20has%20condensed%20all%20different%20weight%20stacks%20into%20a%20single%20motor.%20We%20have%20a%20patent%20for%20this%20motor-controlled%20technology.%20Our%20motor%20provides%20resistance%20from%202%20kg%20to%2075%20kg%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Aman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20150%20exercises%20can%20be%20done%20using%20the%20machine%2C%20and%20every%20muscle%20group%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20body%20can%20be%20targeted.%20AI-powered%20training%20sessions%20track%20the%20user%E2%80%99s%20progress%20and%20suggest%20better%20methods%20of%20working%20out%2C%20while%20giving%20real-time%20tracking%20and%20insights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20machine%20offers%20goal-based%20workout%20programmes%2C%20designed%20by%20professional%20fitness%20trainers.%20From%20building%20muscle%20and%20weight%20training%20to%20becoming%20a%20better%20runner%2C%20the%20machine%20has%20something%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20machine%20comes%20with%20two%20arms%2C%20which%20can%20be%20adjusted%20at%20different%20positions.%20It%20also%20comes%20with%20different%20accessories%20like%20barbells%2C%20ropes%2C%20and%20D-handles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqAldDtor1K%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqAldDtor1K%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E